              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "STRUC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Energies of states in Be-9 giving rise to the",
                " neutron groups were observed,  assuming decay to the",
                " ground state and first excited state of Be-8."
              ]
            }
          ],
